Subject: [PATCH 14/29] Revert "gpio: remove of_get_named_gpio() and
 <linux/of_gpio.h>"

This reverts commit b6420bd5aa0c374331bad6c0fa2eb5f0f87cf5a0.
This is needed for nvidia.

